added to a U.S. State Department assessment of Israeli human rights violations 
against Palestinians. 
</P>
<P>
Jews were beaten, tortured and gassed to death by Nazis simply because they 
were Jews. Blacks are beaten, shot and tortured to death by whites in South 
Africa simply because they are black. Palestinians are beaten, tortured and 
tear-gassed and shot to death by Zionist Israelis in the West Bank and Gaza 
simply because they are Palestinian Arabs. 
</P>
<P>
